release_note: Added formatting features. Adopted Markdown to maintain the strengths of PenCake. Bold italic underline strikethrough highlight headings and horizontal rule are available. We will continue to work hard to add more various formatting elements. Due to technical problems the free trial service has inevitably been terminated. The free trial period you are using will be maintained. We are very sorry for the inconvenience. Italic formatting changed from single slash to double slash . This decision was made to avoid confusion with the slash symbol in everyday use. We apologize for the inconvenience.

Added formatting features. Adopted Markdown to maintain the strengths of PenCake. Bold italic underline strikethrough highlight headings and horizontal rule are available. We will continue to work hard to add more various formatting elements. Due to technical problems the free trial service has inevitably been terminated. The free trial period you are using will be maintained. We are very sorry for the inconvenience.

Now even in the free version you can use Premium fonts and Premium themes. Menu Settings Free Trial Ad Each time you watch an ad you get an additional 12 hours of free use time. Ads can be viewed multiple times a day. The free trial is available again at any time.

Improved sync stability of Google Drive. Fixed bugs occurring in iOS 16. Fixed a bug where it does not scroll to the cursor position when entering edit mode. Fixed a bug where the text layout is different in edit mode and read mode. Added support for iPhone 14 Pro and Pro Max screens.

Improved sync stability of Google Drive. Now PenCake is available to people in more regions. The following languages have been newly added: Spanish Portuguese Brazil Simplified Chinese Traditional Chinese
Now PenCake is available to people in more regions. The following languages have been newly added: Spanish Portuguese Brazil Simplified Chinese Traditional Chinese

URL Detection is now available. Automatically recognize web addresses and emails in articles and display them as clickable links. Web addresses without http and https are not recognized. If you do not want to use this function you can disable it in the Preferences. Fixed an issue that the toolbar is obscured by the home bar of the device when using a Bluetooth keyboard. Fixed a bug where the layout gets broken when editing story titles and folder titles with a Bluetooth keyboard. Fixed the top margin when using landscape mode on iPhone.

The Search feature is here! Added a feature to automatically follow the system s dark mode. Added option to turn Search History on or off. The function to open the search bar with a gesture has been switched to an optional function because many users said that it was inconvenient. Supporting the developer is now available. We appreciate your warm support to continuously improve the app. Menu Settings Tip the Developer

The Search feature is here! Swipe down on the story screen to open the search bar. Supporting the developer is now available. We appreciate your warm support to continuously improve the app. Menu Settings Tip the Developer Fixed some bugs: Fixed a bug where the layout gets broken when using a Bluetooth keyboard on iPad. Fixed a bug where the status bar is not displayed when the system is in dark mode. Fixed some rendering bugs.

Added Undo Redo function. Added larger font sizes and smaller font sizes. You can now omit the subtitle of a story. You can adjust the article width now. Check it out at the Preferences settings. When editing an article you can hide the article title at the top. It can be set in the Preferences settings. Fixed the top and bottom margins on iPhone 12. Fixed a bug where the premium purchase was not completed.

Frequently Asked Questions FAQ page has been opened. Menu Settings FAQs Fixed a bug where the line spacing was narrowed in some fonts. Fixed a bug where the top of the story list was cut off when moving an article. Font settings have unavoidably been reset to fix the font errors. We apologize for the inconvenience. Please download fonts again.

Fonts have been added. Meet the various fonts in the font settings. We will continue to add fonts in the future. Please let us know if there is a font you want. Fixed some bugs Fixed a bug where letters were duplicated when inserting quotation marks while a text block is selected Fixed a bug where the cursor was placed in the wrong place when entering edit mode in a lengthy article Fixed a bug where Google login was not possible on iOS 9 and iOS 10
Improved sync stability of Google Drive. Fixed some bugs related to the sync.

Square size added to Cover Image. Fixed a bug that scrolled to the beginning or end all at once when selecting a range outside the screen in writing mode. Fixed the lag when moving the cursor using an extended key. Fixed an error when canceling Google Drive login.

Sync feature released! Auto sync is available. Premium Manual sync is also very convenient. iCloud and Google Drive are supported. Purchase history is also synced. Story folder feature added. You can group stories by category. Try it on the story list. Trash feature added. If you delete an article it will stay in the Trash. The Trash can be seen in the story list. Change history feature added. You can check the change history for each article and restore a previous version. You can change the way you open the story list to short tap. Try the Preferences settings. Left justification is now possible. The default alignment can be specified in the Preferences settings Article moving is now for free. Improved the date picker UI. Year selection is now available. You can now set as the current time. Fixed a bug where text is not visible. Fixed a bug displaying the wrong cloud status

Now Pencake is available in Japanese! If there is a mistake in Japanese please let us know. : A bigger font size has been added. Fixed a bug where the photo size didn t change on SplitView and Landscape mode. Fixed a bug where the top and bottom of the menu were cut off in landscape mode.

You can now insert photos in the body of an article. Please tap the photo icon in edit mode. The cover image can be turned on and off. You can now double tap and go directly to a specific paragraph. Preview feature has been added. Expanded keyboard functionality has been enhanced. Ellipsis bullet parenthesis paragraph navigation and preview have been added. You can see the tooltips again. Tap See Tooltips Again at Settings. Fixed bugs where... A photo is not attached when selecting the original photo option. A screen jumps up when inserting quotation marks. The article view scrolls to the top after editing. Some Chinese characters are not shown in the correct font.

When backing up a txt file is not created any more. Display error codes when the backup and restore fail.
Changed the default photo option from Original to Fixed Size

New features The Original Photo option added. You can now add a photo without cropping. A GIF autoplays on the article view. Big improvements in Export and Share You can export each story or article as a ZIP that bundles the photos and the TXTs. Separate files are also available for the article sharing. To edit an article double tap anywhere on the article view. Improvements Improved the autosave performance. We expect lags during writing to be resolved. Extended the bottom area of the article view for iPhone X series.

Icon renewal The icon has been renewed! We hope you like it! : New features A sans serif font has beed added. Premium You can set the font at Settings Fonts . Try the premium features. You can try the new font and the dark mode each for 1 minute. Try it right now! You can try it again and again. Check the auto save status. If you stop typing for a while it will be auto saved. When the auto save is completed the Done button changes to blue. Improvements Larger font size Character count is now default for Chinese and Japanese Moved the photo icon to the right side Bug fixes Fixed content clipping at the both sides of the screen in landscape Fixed slowed down saving at the last update
